CompositeTimeInterval can be seen as a list and union of SimpleTimeIntervals.
Its simplification is S_1 ∪ (S_2 ∪ (S_3 ∪ (...)))), where S_i is one of its intervals. As long as it does not contain any cyclic dependency it should be fine.
